videos.description: Eli Stove takes the hand off on the jet sweep and goes untouched for 78 yards to the end zone putting Auburn up in a hurry 7-0.
videos.headline: Auburn needs only one play to go 78 yards for a TD

videos.description: Sean White run for 41 yds to the Ark 22 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: S. White run for 41 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Auburn goes 91 yards in 10 plays, capping it off when Kamryn Pettway goes right through an Arkansas defender and scores from nine yards out upping the score to 14-0 Tigers.
videos.headline: Pettway runs over defender en route to another Auburn TD

videos.description: Austin Allen run for 11 yds to the Ark 27 Austin Allen fumbled, recovered by Aub Marlon Davidson
videos.headline: Austin Allen pump fakes ball into ground for fumble

videos.description: Stanton Truitt becomes the third Auburn player to score a rushing touchdown in the first quarter as the Tigers zoom out to a 21-0 lead on Arkansas.
videos.headline: Auburn makes it three rushing TDs in the first quarter

videos.description: Arkansas quarterback Austin Allen stayed on the ground holding his knee after completing a short pass to Austin Cantrell
videos.headline: Austin Allen injured after short completion

videos.description: Sean White pass complete to Stanton Truitt for 45 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Truitt left wide open for 45-yard TD
McFain 54 yard field goal gets Arkansas on the board

videos.description: Auburn increases the lead when Sean White keeps it on the run-option and coasts into the end zone putting the Tigers up 35-3.
videos.headline: White's fourth down keeper finds the end zone for Auburn

videos.description: Austin Allen pass intercepted Javaris Davis return for no gain to the Aub 31
videos.headline: Auburn's Davis makes juggling interception

videos.description: Auburn makes it five rushing touchdowns on the day, this one from 23 yards out for Kamryn Pettway's second of the game that gets the seal of approval from Tigers' legend Bo Jackson.
videos.headline: Another Auburn rushing TD gets Bo Jackson's approval

videos.description: The rout continues for Auburn as Stanton Truitt breaks through the line and is gone for his third touchdown of the night pushing the Tigers lead to 49-3.
videos.headline: Auburn's Truitt makes it a hat-trick of touchdowns

videos.description: Kam Martin run for 51 yds for a TD
videos.headline: K. Martin run for 51 yds for a TD

videos.description: Auburn WR Stanton Truitt scores his first three touchdowns as a Tiger in dramatic fashion during a 56-3 win over Arkansas.
videos.headline: Tigers offense breaks through

videos.description: No. 21 Auburn rushes for 543 yards and seven touchdowns against No. 17 Arkansas as the Tigers win 56-3.
videos.headline: Auburn runs over Arkansas

videos.description: Auburn set an SEC conference-game record with 543 rush yards against Arkansas, including a 78-yard touchdown by Eli Stove on the Tigers' first snap. Gus Malzahn and Bret Bielema offer their perspective on the first strike in Auburn's 56-3 rout.
videos.headline: Malzahn explains Auburn's tone-setting, first-play TD
